From f5f1c08ea5efa0845135b20da78adce49f8ddfb0 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Robin <robin@phyta.org>
Date: Sun, 24 May 2026 18:44:51 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] feat(firmware): add structured 3012 publish-failure context

Classify MQTT publish failures into cb_open/queue_shed/outbox_full/transport_error and attach topic, gpio, and sensor_type context to 3012 error payloads so AUT-456 can persist and correlate them.

Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>
---
